67

         */
69

        /**
71 
         * @param array Array to operate on.
72 
         * @param startIndex Index of the first element to take into account.

         * @param numElements Number of elements to take into account.

         * @return the result of the operation.
75 
         */
76

77

78 
                        int numElements);

    }
